summary: Ake Wennmatm, M.D. was born January 22, 1943, in Stockholm, Sweden. He is married to Marianne Junstad and has three children. His doctorate degree is from the Karolinska Institute, Stockholm,. He was a member of the Royal Swedish Academy of Medicine.
